Durban - A 28-year-old woman has appeared in the Durban Magistrate’s Court for murdering 10-year-old Njabulo Mankayi and his best friend, Luyanda Msomi.ADVERTISINGinRead invented by Teads
Appearing disheveled, Amahle Bongiwe Maliwa was charged with two counts each of murder, kidnapping and assault with intent to do grievous bodily harm.
The court heard on Monday that the State would oppose bail.













